title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Toys, Games, Sports Eqp. & Parts & Acces.
description: Imports Intra Eu - Toys, Games, Sports Eqp. & Parts & Acces. in the United Kingdom increased to 128.28 GBP Million in September from 112.87 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Toys, Games, Sports Eqp. & Part in the United Kingdom averaged 73.79 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 375.68 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 16.99 GBP Million in January of 1999.
